SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Grain Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA GRAIN REGULATIONS in order to make consequential amendments to the Canada Grain Regulations and accompanying schedules to align them with amendments to the Canada Grain Act contained in the Marketing Freedom for Grain Farmers Act and to make an additional housekeeping change to improve clarity and ease of use.
